titles.title: A bill to suspend temporarily the duty on 2,2-Dimethylbutanoic acid 3-(2,4-dichlorophenyl)-2oxo-1-oxaspiro(4.5)dec-3-en-4-yl ester.

action.text: Read twice and referred to the Committee on Finance.

bill.summary: 11/2/2009--Introduced. Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to suspend temporarily the duty on 2,2-Dimethylbutanoic acid 3-(2,4-dichlorophenyl)-2oxo-1-oxaspiro(4.5)dec-3-en-4-yl ester.
